# MVP Scope & Requirements

## MVP Goal

Deliver a usable, local-first pentest notebook that feels intelligent through **state-aware suggestions**, without automation or AI exploitation.

## In Scope (MVP)

### Knowledge Base

* Markdown-based notes
* Categories:

  * Ports & Services
  * Methodology
  * Techniques / Playbooks
* Tagging and search

### Engagements (Case Files)

* Create/edit engagements
* Define targets (IP/host)
* Track open ports and services
* Add free-form findings

### Methodology Tracking

* Fixed phases:

  1. Reconnaissance
  2. Enumeration
  3. Exploitation
  4. Post-Exploitation
* Manual phase selection

### Suggestions

* Rule-based next-step suggestions
* Based on phase + services + findings

## Out of Scope (MVP)

* Command execution
* Auto-exploitation
* Collaboration
* Cloud sync
* AI-generated payloads

## Definition of Done

* User can manage KB
* User can manage engagements
* State updates correctly
* Suggestions change with context
